properties.name: The High Road
properties.description:
There are times when, through necessity or laziness, one is compelled to take the low road. But we'll not stoop to that level; not this week.

This week is all about taking the high road. It is not always the highest of roads -- indeed, sometimes it is not even a road at all -- but it is certainly the higher one, given the available choices.
